SEARCH
Package research

Class ResearchJournal

java.lang.Object
research.ResearchJournal
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ResearchJournal extends Object implements Serializable
The ResearchJournal class represents a research journal in the system. It contains information about the journal, such as its name, editors, section, published papers, subscribers, and average rating.
